Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.04,0:15:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 春香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔 製作人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作人你一個人努力過頭了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.49,0:15:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.66,0:15:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.91,0:15:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 請相信我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.21,0:15:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 拜託妳們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 那邊要小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…稍微再等一下另外一個人就會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.84,0:15:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞蹈動作 沒時間就為了她單獨再教一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.68,0:15:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.16,0:15:57.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說妳 事到如今再來已經沒妳的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:15:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿真 讓美希看看舞是怎麼跳的
