Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以教我接下來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 我這是在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:17:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「請相信我們」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.51,0:17:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 所以…
